snippet: Four games into the season, the Jets’ offense has scored one touchdown in its last 34 possessions, and Mark Sanchez has the worst completion percentage among starting quarterbacks, at 49.2.
abstract: New York Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez, who has the worst completion percentage among starting quarterbacks this season, brushes off criticism as team prepares to face Houston Texans.
lead_paragraph: Four games into the season, the Jets’ offense has scored one touchdown in its last 34 possessions, and Mark Sanchez has the worst completion percentage among starting quarterbacks, at 49.2.
